description:
This is a 60 minute workout called 'Running Mix 2020 | 135 - 160 BPM | Best Running Music' from the channel Spinnin' Records.
The workout falls under Cardio/Running.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: In many countries the complete lockdowns due to COVID-19 are being lifted, which in many cases means we can finally go back out to work out again! One of our favorite attributes to a good run is listening to some good music and that’s why we’ve made this mix! This mix is perfect for the more advanced runners who run at a higher tempo. Enjoy!
